metadata.name: COMMUNITY BUILDING - 3D Polaroid
metadata.description:
Community building has been an eye-opening art form. It is gritty, humbling work. It takes time and intention. There’s something special about being able to organize and motivate folks around you. 

I see a lot of myself reflected in this young person. Each part of their outfit is an indicator of the path ahead. 

The empty red bucket - a symbol of Faith - knowing you won’t have to carry it forever. But also knowing that it is a necessary tool for gathering resources for the community you’re working to uplift. 
The shoes stepping out of the frame - symbolizing how one must step outside of the box in order to move forward toward change.
The gold circle framed glasses - for a clear vision of your growing dream. 

Artist: Raven50mm

Medium: Digital Photography

Edition: 1/1
